column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY PICNIC CHOCOLATE BAR MILK CHOCOLATE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 05000312002131
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: Sugar, PEANUTS, glucose syrup, glucose-fructose syrup, dried grapes, WHEAT flour (with added calcium, iron, niacin and thiamin), palm oil, cocoa butter, dried whey (from MILK), cocoa mass, dried skimmed MILK, rice flour, MILK fat, emulsifiers (E442, sunflower lecithin, E476, E471, SOYA lecithin), salt, BARLEY malt extract, raising agent (sodium bicarbonate, ammonium bicarbonate), maize flour, anti-caking agent (calcium carbonate), flavourings, MILK proteins. MILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 14% MINIMUM.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER.. MAY CONTAIN NUTS, EGG. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 09/09/2017
